high_descs: Take few steps front and turn left and again take a left turn to reach the sink on the right side
Take a knife from the sink
Little bit move towards the left side of the counter top
Cut a potato into pieces
Little bit move towards the right side
Put the knife on the counter top
Turn and stand in front of the counter top
Take a potato piece from the cut potato
Turn right and take few steps and  again turn right and walk straight to reach the microwave oven on the right side
Open the oven and put the potato piece into the oven and close it. After few seconds, open the door and take the potato piece out and again close the oven.
Turn right and walk straight and reach the fridge on the right side
Open the fridge and put the potato piece inside and close the fridge
anns.task_desc: Put the potato piece in the fridge

high_descs: Turn around move towards the sink.
Take the knife from the sink.
Turn around move towards the counter top.
Cut the potato with the knife.
Turn around move towards the counter top.
Keep the knife on the counter top.
Turn around move towards the counter top.
Take the potato from the counter top.
Turn around move towards the microwave.
Keep the potato inside and get back from microwave.
Turn around move towards the fridge.
Keep the potato inside of the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Take the knife, cut the potato ,keep it on the microwave and keep it on the microwave.

high_descs: Go around the counters to your left to go to the sink.
Pick up the knife from the sink.
Go to the counter to the left of the sink.
Slice the potato on the counter.
Look to the counter area next to the potato.
Place the knife down.
Look back to the potato you sliced.
Pick up a single potato slice.
Walk back around the counters and go to the microwave on the table ahead and to the right.
Microwave the potato slice and pick it back up.
Go back to the kitchen and stop at the fridge on the right corner.
Place the potato slice in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved potato slice in a fridge.
